emails.subject: Welcome
emails.content:
<%- __('Thank you for becoming a member of Slotser! We hope that you enjoy playing our slots and wish you the best of luck!') %>

<% if(typeof(password) !== 'undefined'){ %>
    <%- __("Your slotser.com password:") %> <%- password %>
<% } %>

<%- __("Have fun and good luck!") %>

<%- __("Sincerely,") %>

<%- __("- Slotser Team") %>
https://www.slotser.com/
